  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Construction Yards allow construction of new ships and
  bases. They also provide facilities for repair and retrofit of existing s=
hips
  and bases. Construction Yard components are typically incorporated into s=
pace
  ports.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>As your research in Construction progresses you gain the
  following benefits:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list=
:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;
  mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'><sp=
an
  style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Ro=
man"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-langu=
age:
  EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>increase the maximum size of ships and bases you =
can
  build<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpLast style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;
  mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'><sp=
an
  style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Ro=
man"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-langu=
age:
  EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>increase the speed at which you construct ships a=
nd
  bases<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>When a new construction technology is researched, ALL
  construction yards are automatically upgraded so that they can build LARG=
ER
  ships and bases.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <h3><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'=
>Colony
  construction yards<o:p></o:p></span></h3>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>In addition to construction yards at space ports, each
  colony also has a single built-in construction yard for building bases,
  colony ships, resupply ships and construction ships</span>. Colony ships,
  construction ships, resupply ships and space ports can ONLY be built at
  colony construction yards. As your colony grows, the construction speed of
  its built-in construction yard also increases.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Note that bases built at colonies (e.g. space ports)=
 are
  not subject to size restrictions. Any size base may be built at a colony,
  regardless of current construction technology level.<span lang=3DEN-GB
  style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
